OL,3,CConclave: How is a new Pope elected?
OL,5,FFor centuries, leaders of the Roman
OL,6,FCatholic Church have been chosen at
OL,7,Fthe Vatican in private gatherings
OL,8,Fknown as conclaves.
OL,10,FThe historic vote is shrouded in
OL,11,Fsecrecy.
OL,13,FThe conclave to elect a new pope will
OL,14,Fbegin on Wednesday, May 7, the Vatican
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FThe Cardinals present in Rome decided
OL,18,Fon the date at their fifth General
OL,19,FCongregation.
OL,21,FWho can be pope?
