OL,3,CConclave: How is a new Pope elected?
OL,5,FThe process is repeated twice more,
OL,6,Fand if there is still a stalemate, the
OL,7,Fchamberlain will declare that a result
OL,8,Fcan come from an absolute majority or
OL,9,Fby a vote on the two names that
OL,10,Freceived the largest number of votes
OL,11,Fin the last ballot.
OL,13,FOnce a candidate has been chosen, they
OL,14,Fare called to the front of the chapel
OL,15,Fand asked whether they are willing to
OL,16,Faccept.
OL,18,FIf the answer is yes, the new pope is
OL,19,Fthen asked to choose his new papal
OL,20,Fname.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
