OL,3,CConclave: How is a new Pope elected?
OL,5,FThere are no rules around selecting
OL,6,Fthe papal name, however, the name
OL,7,Fchosen by the Pope often reflects a
OL,8,Fpredecessor they admire or is linked
OL,9,Fto a revered saint, and can signify
OL,10,Fthe values they will focus on.
OL,12,FWhen is the new pope announced?
OL,14,FAfter each round of voting, the
OL,15,Fballots are burned with chemicals to
OL,16,Fmake the smoke either black, meaning
OL,17,Fno decision has been reached or white,
OL,18,Fsignalling a pope has been elected.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
